key_misc_profiles.name: Xenophon A. Galinas
key_misc_profiles.summary: Negotiated lease on former Iranian consulate townhouse 34 E 69th St March 1996. Proposed arrangement included Epstein payment of $100k for improvements. Career in ship building with General Dynamics. Director: FreeSeas Inc, Manhattan Maritime Enterprises, ASA Holdings, Williston SA, Benzopetrol SA. Education: BS University of Surrey, MS Marine Engineering U Michigan, MBA Finance NYU.

key_misc_profiles.name: Vlad Doronin
key_misc_profiles.summary: Allegedly JE's client, boyfriend to Naomi Campbell (Lolita Express passenger). International businessman and real estate developer. 1985 relocated to Geneva then Zug, worked under Marc Rich. Founder/chairman Capital Group Moscow, owner/chairman Aman, chairman/CEO OKO Group.

key_misc_profiles.name: Ralph Cioffi
key_misc_profiles.summary: Former Bear Stearns hedge fund manager. Arrested June 19 2008 with Matthew Tannin charged with securities fraud (accused of misleading investors about subprime mortgage market). Epstein lost $57M as 'Major Investor No. 1'. Cioffi never met Epstein at Bear Stearns. Found not guilty Nov 2009, case acquitted.

key_misc_profiles.name: Matthew Tannin
key_misc_profiles.summary: Former Bear Stearns hedge fund manager. Arrested with Cioffi June 19 2008 charged securities fraud. Never met Epstein. Found not guilty Nov 2009, case acquitted.

key_misc_profiles.name: Michael Reiter
key_misc_profiles.summary: PB Police Chief during JE's arrest. Complained JE received 'unusual treatment'. Lead detective in David Kennedy 1984 drug overdose death. Worked William Kennedy Smith 1991 rape investigation. Master's degree human resource development Palm Beach Atlantic U. FBI National Academy Quantico. Top secret national security clearance.

key_misc_profiles.name: Scott Lipps
key_misc_profiles.summary: Next Model Management employee through family connection. 1997 moved to NY, hired by Karin to revamp office. Feuded with JLB, walked out. 2002 started One Management in TriBeCa. 2011 tapped by Courtney Love to be drummer for Hole.

key_misc_profiles.name: Conchita Sarnoff
key_misc_profiles.summary: Author of TrafficKing (published May 2016) about sexual abuse of minors, focus on Jeffrey Epstein. Daughter of Pedro Suarez Hernandez (architectural/engineering company Madrid and Miami) and Conchita Priete Suarez of Spain. Grandmother related to Spanish Royal family. Columbia and Yale. Executive Director Alliance to Rescue Victims of Trafficking (ATRVT). 1984 married Daniel Jay Sarnoff (b 1956, grandson of David Sarnoff d 1971), divorced, one daughter Christina.
